                <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Curing & Protection</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500">Maintain moisture for proper curing (7 days minimum). Strip forms after 24-48 hours. Install drainage before backfilling. Document for inspections.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
