                <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Masonry Walls:</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-cyan-600 mr-2">✓</span>
                    <span>Tooled mortar joints preferred</span>
